cmnyogyjb00a1udsg0cffqkip	cmnyoay6c002ludsgggexia88	medalert-cameroun-n121	MedAlert Cameroun	Alertes médicales et rappels de traitements via SMS et WhatsApp	\N	HEALTH	IDEA	\N	Cameroun	Yaoundé	\N	LOCAL	Au Cameroun, 60% des patients chroniques oublient ou arrêtent prématurément leur traitement. Les médecins n'ont aucun moyen de suivi entre les consultations.	Patients chroniques (diabète, hypertension) et centres de santé, environ 2 millions de patients	Les patients comptent sur leur mémoire ou un proche. Certains collent des post-its.	Système de rappels automatisés via SMS et WhatsApp pour les prises de médicaments. Le médecin programme le protocole, le patient reçoit les rappels sans avoir besoin de smartphone.	Fonctionne par SMS basique — pas besoin de smartphone ni d'internet	Pas de téléconsultation, pas de pharmacie en ligne, pas de diagnostic	B2B	SUBSCRIPTION	MyDawa (Kenya) nécessite un smartphone. Aucune solution SMS-first au Cameroun.	CEO	10-20H	Discussions avec 5 centres de santé à Yaoundé	TECH,BIZ	EQUITY	Couvrir 100 centres de santé au Cameroun en 2 ans et réduire l'abandon de traitement de 40%.	\N	\N	{}	\N	\N	\N	{"Twilio/SMS API","WhatsApp Business API",Node.js,"Dashboard React"}	{}	\N	\N	f	f	PUBLISHED	[0.10241643,-0.06426635,0.03846377,-0.02509369,0.12725024,-0.11086519,0.01506804,0.15618189,-0.02749786,-0.09122679,-0.02244373,0.10856834,-0.00386983,0.06984279,0.00292319,-0.03002526,-0.08939781,-0.01556865,-0.0676607,0.06820638,0.02093311,-0.0071986,-0.0357478,0.08531451,-0.1573189,-0.05481767,-0.04945704,0.0451271,-0.203534,-0.00109083,-0.04070262,-0.17260222,0.00205697,-0.04027122,-0.0191966,0.06776859,-0.01412016,-0.01136801,-0.03769638,-0.01238658,0.00657288,0.05856873,0.00417163,-0.00078192,0.09644295,-0.02186408,-0.02966312,-0.01861204,-0.02422074,0.01309629,-0.04522786,0.07429812,0.00746192,0.01475358,0.03805627,-0.05034793,-0.07878602,-0.03398087,-0.01010822,0.01026327,-0.00013744,0.00522245,0.08870845,-0.02502964,0.00146706,-0.00437962,0.06197666,-