cmnyojmdf00ecudsgpbmnmien	cmnyob0lb002rudsgmxrfmffv	comptasimple-tqw0	ComptaSimple	Comptabilité simplifiée pour PME camerounaises	\N	FINTECH	PROTOTYPE	\N	Cameroun	Douala	\N	LOCAL	Les PME camerounaises tiennent leur comptabilité sur papier ou Excel. 80% ne sont pas conformes fiscalement, risquant des amendes de 500 000 à 5 000 000 FCFA.	PME et micro-entreprises camerounaises, environ 200 000 structures formelles	Excel, cahiers papier, ou comptables freelance à 50 000 FCFA/mois	Application web et mobile de comptabilité simplifiée conforme au plan OHADA. Génération automatique des déclarations fiscales DGI.	Conforme OHADA nativement, génère les déclarations DGI en 1 clic	Pas de conseil fiscal personnalisé, pas d'audit comptable	B2B	SAAS	QuickBooks trop complexe et en anglais. Wave pas adapté au plan OHADA.	CEO	FULLTIME	30 PME en beta test à Douala, taux de rétention 85%	TECH	EQUITY	Digitaliser la comptabilité de 50 000 PME en zone CEMAC en 3 ans.	\N	\N	{}	\N	\N	\N	{React,Node.js,PostgreSQL,"Comptabilité OHADA"}	{}	\N	\N	f	f	PUBLISHED	[0.162939,-0.08430751,0.0639926,0.00738341,-0.02080234,0.06096629,0.02070536,0.09703536,0.04181999,-0.005214,-0.04521912,0.08194988,-0.03214321,-0.0268064,-0.02362196,-0.13771647,-0.1130373,0.1519741,0.03414374,0.04108863,-0.06005624,0.00887631,0.04779711,0.05045437,-0.12313237,-0.05308155,-0.11112741,0.09570614,-0.07833884,-0.06539451,0.06287209,-0.09187239,-0.02516425,-0.0512404,-0.04941053,0.07068621,0.07212182,0.04042766,-0.04536757,-0.00084112,0.08298761,-0.03893432,0.03155381,-0.05240113,0.03042047,-0.00194992,0.00786419,0.01882026,0.06117876,-0.03465605,-0.02541659,-0.01477489,0.02913068,0.03954618,-0.00452023,-0.09207761,-0.02565787,-0.05209054,-0.04838418,-0.02512597,0.05229313,0.03937751,0.04441619,-0.04541558,-0.00577992,-0.01155598,0.01170967,-0.04060826,0.01081507,-0.03841642,-0.00277739,-0.03400237,0.02300359,0.04193977,-0.02039841,0.0002685,0.01088797,0.0133415,0.00269801,0.0089177,-0.01021863,0.00530996,-0.03986533,0.029359