cmnyokycm00gjudsgd9qnv7fd	cmnyob1vl002uudsgrk5gj2wf	schoolpay-05o3	SchoolPay	Paiement de scolarité par mobile money en plusieurs fois	\N	EDTECH	PROTOTYPE	\N	Cameroun	Yaoundé	\N	LOCAL	Les parents camerounais peinent à payer la scolarité en une fois (100 000 à 500 000 FCFA). Les écoles souffrent d'impayés chroniques.	Parents d'élèves et établissements scolaires privés, environ 3 000 écoles	Paiements en espèces fragmentés, nombreux conflits et exclusions d'élèves	Plateforme de paiement de scolarité en plusieurs versements par mobile money. L'école reçoit un paiement consolidé mensuel.	Paiement en 3-10 fois sans frais pour les parents, consolidation pour les écoles	Pas de crédit scolaire, pas de gestion pédagogique	B2B	COMMISSION	\N	CEO	FULLTIME	2 écoles pilotes, 150 parents inscrits	TECH,FINANCE	EQUITY	Couvrir 1000 écoles au Cameroun et réduire les impayés de 50%.	\N	\N	{}	\N	\N	\N	{"Mobile Money API",React,Node.js,Accounting}	{}	\N	\N	f	f	PUBLISHED	[0.04240938,-0.15823169,0.13196816,-0.03770115,-0.00468682,-0.02257425,-0.00689339,0.14303587,0.07081112,-0.09526108,0.01189502,0.01465796,-0.01704465,-0.05756986,-0.06343352,-0.06524973,-0.13783771,0.15085147,0.01040578,0.03495889,0.04549633,0.03073834,0.00435857,0.08700751,-0.07595158,-0.08514933,-0.1485435,0.07572472,-0.10942358,0.00872718,0.05912625,-0.07777042,-0.00555812,-0.02348285,-0.04503503,-0.00162254,-0.00251633,-0.02326533,-0.18290591,0.02809709,0.02163668,0.04858618,-0.06027253,0.04216561,-0.01780448,0.00939068,-0.03156519,-0.01358156,-0.00390264,-0.01197436,-0.02891401,0.02113923,-0.01196649,-0.02362622,0.02504152,-0.08814706,0.0152905,0.05280075,-0.01516405,0.04034998,0.03949432,0.02781019,0.11274389,-0.0436639,-0.03106879,0.01651225,0.01090518,-0.0292834,0.02910531,-0.01409987,-0.03578421,-0.0487306,0.07256849,0.00524332,0.00885901,-0.0422229,0.02711981,0.00034078,-0.06945913,-0.09347897,0.03013537,0.01222761,0.04620528,0.01019248,-0.02007066,0.09548402,0.01027952,-0.00145887,-0.01567103,0.07697377,-0.03470