cmnyoqa0x00p6udsgi5kx8ro0	cmnyob6he0036udsg340c0ttc	transfertdirect-zo4d	TransfertDirect	Transfert d'argent P2P sans frais entre le Cameroun et l'Europe	\N	FINTECH	MVP_BUILD	\N	Cameroun	Douala	\N	DIASPORA	Les frais de transfert d'argent vers le Cameroun sont de 7-10% en moyenne. Sur 500 milliards FCFA envoyés par an, 40 milliards partent en frais.	Diaspora camerounaise en Europe envoyant de l'argent au pays	Western Union (8-10%), World Remit (5-7%), transfert informel via des particuliers	Système P2P de matching : un utilisateur en France veut envoyer des euros au Cameroun, un commerçant camerounais veut payer un fournisseur en France. On matche les flux.	Frais de 1% maximum grâce au matching de flux inversés	Pas de crypto, pas de compte bancaire, pas de carte prépayée	B2C	COMMISSION	Wise (3%), Wave (2% mais limité), aucun ne fait le matching P2P	CEO	FULLTIME	100 utilisateurs beta en France-Cameroun, 15 millions FCFA transférés	TECH,FINANCE	EQUITY	Devenir le corridor de transfert le moins cher entre l'Europe et l'Afrique Centrale.	\N	\N	{}	\N	\N	\N	{Node.js,React,"Banking/Compliance APIs",Security}	{}	\N	\N	f	f	PUBLISHED	[0.05660513,-0.18227297,0.026489,-0.0769395,0.0716575,0.07960692,0.03002791,0.1330268,0.0776565,-0.07527059,-0.02256108,0.07211252,0.05365695,-0.02855599,-0.06744086,-0.0937614,-0.13430147,0.06055449,-0.03616797,-0.03053782,0.05218738,0.05813564,0.0211205,0.07609483,-0.14697456,-0.0257605,-0.04090035,0.12489263,-0.13397871,0.05154962,0.03557628,0.00630717,-0.00045963,-0.04542737,-0.13725117,0.03786995,-0.05113589,0.0347537,-0.12184412,0.04167607,0.0371937,0.00617891,-0.00385406,0.01649569,0.12408575,0.0125663,0.0062631,-0.0444851,0.02677913,0.01190728,-0.06158735,-5.697e-05,0.01568898,-0.06749416,0.08254986,-0.02045375,-0.02999548,0.01374211,0.00774381,0.03508848,0.07706321,0.01322297,0.09761884,0.02508507,0.03258496,0.00454454,0.03713727,-0.04463536,0.0445553,-0.04050038,-0.0606062,-0.02108533,0.06340743,0.01179217,-0.00382559,-7.363e-05,0.05577705