cmnyorm2p00rdudsg68xg1suc	cmnyob7ld0039udsgsmryphgz	saferide-cm-5ucl	SafeRide CM	Covoiturage sécurisé pour les trajets interurbains	\N	LOGISTICS	IDEA	\N	Cameroun	Yaoundé	\N	LOCAL	Les trajets Yaoundé-Douala coûtent 5000 FCFA en bus et 4h. Les voitures particulières font le trajet avec des places vides mais sans moyen de les proposer.	Voyageurs réguliers sur les axes interurbains camerounais	\N	Application de covoiturage pour les trajets interurbains. Vérification du conducteur par CNI, assurance trajet, paiement mobile money.	Covoiturage vérifié et assuré — plus sûr et 40% moins cher que le bus	\N	B2C	COMMISSION	\N	CEO	10-20H	\N	TECH,BIZ	EQUITY	Devenir le BlaBlaCar de l'Afrique Centrale avec 100 000 trajets par mois.	\N	\N	{}	\N	\N	\N	{"React Native",Maps/GPS,Node.js,"Insurance API"}	{}	\N	\N	f	f	PUBLISHED	[-0.03312189,-0.18538328,0.07229443,-0.03983092,0.04234381,0.00876005,-0.00624807,0.1859022,-0.04252505,-0.14738691,-0.03271287,0.03329407,0.08106884,-0.03810429,0.00280447,-0.1459644,-0.14418402,0.11291999,-0.13517027,0.03437158,-0.00581379,0.00391807,-0.08819149,0.05779472,-0.08079485,-0.0224323,0.04264387,0.06480385,-0.07961166,0.06583384,0.05021021,0.02274296,-0.03572759,0.01655442,0.01597978,0.00148266,-0.00013556,-0.03798693,-0.04675804,0.03415994,0.02496685,-0.00945778,0.02916041,-0.00329269,0.03790271,-0.02744919,-0.00416228,0.04235198,-0.00168941,-0.06651098,-0.09648501,-0.04133449,-0.02667651,0.05418178,0.03433027,-0.07016736,0.01821335,-0.06680818,0.01272408,-0.00497824,0.02436065,0.00245704,0.04652993,-0.03884574,-0.01493299,-0.0016136,0.09061826,-0.05301309,0.01235281,0.0333097,-0.01586623,-0.02669049,0.05661083,0.02106879,0.04139952,-0.0662862,-0.00235613,-0.01414313,-0.02113252,-0.05318014,0.04027343,0.03013717,0.00132083,-0.02160784,-0.07366354,0.06504122,0.00618461,0.0704257,-0.05288302,0.00940803,0.04106842,-0.11333042,0.06314985,0.05634711,0.03946337,0.01269921,0.04420324,-0.07459706,0.01645219,0.01437408,-0.04348919,-0.02995212,-0.0169273,0.0382