cmnyosxz300tiudsgzh9vmikx	cmnyob8p3003cudsgwb1sufx0	cleanwater-cm-s5kx	CleanWater CM	Monitoring IoT de la qualité de l'eau potable	\N	HEALTH	PROTOTYPE	\N	Cameroun	Douala	\N	LOCAL	L'eau du robinet à Douala est souvent impropre à la consommation. Les citoyens n'ont aucun moyen de vérifier la qualité en temps réel.	Communautés urbaines et péri-urbaines, sociétés de distribution d'eau	Bouillir l'eau, acheter de l'eau minérale (300-500 FCFA/jour/famille) ou boire sans vérifier	Capteurs IoT installés aux points d'eau stratégiques. Dashboard de suivi de la qualité (turbidité, pH, chlore) accessible au public et aux autorités.	Monitoring continu et alertes automatiques quand l'eau devient impropre	\N	B2G	SAAS	Aucun acteur IoT water quality en Afrique Centrale	CTO	FULLTIME	5 capteurs installés dans 2 quartiers de Douala, données collectées depuis 3 mois	BIZ	EQUITY	Monitorer la qualité de l'eau de 50 villes africaines en 5 ans.	\N	\N	{}	\N	\N	\N	{IoT/Embedded,"Data Visualization",Node.js,Hardware}	{}	\N	\N	f	f	PUBLISHED	[0.0521121,-0.07612241,0.090073,-0.06868434,0.11071791,-0.0513983,-0.0346854,0.12014217,-0.06923659,0.02352559,-0.0986834,0.08067154,0.05545979,0.01038382,-0.00954497,-0.18424489,-0.09276532,0.11222935,0.01679983,-0.00668152,-0.03259961,-0.04537083,0.01513184,0.07566419,-0.17326587,0.00569539,0.07618824,0.0572511,-0.12666437,0.02352737,0.08682215,-0.03188965,0.09799494,-0.00363803,-0.06301502,0.00895827,0.05359404,-0.01867598,-0.02136429,-0.06547054,0.0480531,-0.00035868,-0.02695158,-0.09010947,0.10012417,0.03111359,0.01775294,0.07402509,-0.04305826,-0.04163037,-0.04410054,0.0292395,-0.03195626,0.02061855,0.00371855,-0.0557029,0.01493836,-0.02366524,-0.00830836,-0.02098095,-0.03814869,0.03435399,0.0065684,-0.02632481,-0.05559504,0.00057801,0.01340259,-0.08689713,-0.03028787,0.01703904,-0.0155515,0.03817291,-0.02882709,-0.07967702,0.01288121,-0.00440752,-0.03011341,-0.01613043,-0.05102225,-0.06702187,0.01406582,0.02129997,0.03666204,-0.01981311,-0.02065709,0.02